rect>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>For flow-based inspection, NTurbo establishes a dedicated data path to redirect traffic between the IPS engine and FortiGate ingress and egress interfaces.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct><percent-correct>100</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer></answers></question-record><question-record><question>Which two statements about the Security Fabric rating are true? (Choose two.)</question><clue></clue><category></category><weighting>100</weighting><fixed>0</fixed><question-type>4</question-type><answers><answer><text>A license is required to obtain an executive summary in the Security Rating section.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct><percent-correct>100</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>The Security Posture category provides PCI compliance results.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>The root FortiGate provides executive summaries of all the FortiGate devices in the Security Fabric.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct><percent-correct>100</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>Security Rating Insights are available only in the Security Rating page.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer></answers><must-select-all>1</must-select-all></question-record><question-record><question>An administrator has configured a dialup IPsec VPN on FortiGate with add-route enabled. However, the static route is not showing in the routing table.</question><clue></clue><category></category><weighting>100</weighting><fixed>0</fixed><question-type>4</question-type><answers><answer>