Based on the exhibits, what is the possible cause of the issue? 
&amp;#x003C;img src=&quot;67.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;67.jpg&quot; title=&quot;67&quot; width=&quot;1231&quot; height=&quot;496&quot; style=&quot;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;&quot;/&amp;#x003E;</question><clue></clue><category></category><weighting>100</weighting><fixed>0</fixed><question-type>1</question-type><answers><answer><text>The web rating override configuration is incorrect</text><feedback></feedback><correct>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>The web filter profile feature set is configured incorrectly.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>The firewall policy inspection mode is incorrect.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct><percent-correct>100</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer><answer><text>For www. facebook. com. the URL filter action is incorrect.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>0</correct><percent-correct>0</percent-correct><include-in-mc-options>1</include-in-mc-options></answer></answers></question-record></questions>
